{"pdfData":[[{"bbox":[196,127,389,147],"type":"title","angle":0,"index":0,"text":"# 第12章 振动传感器","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"level":1,"page_idx":0,"id":"87c0dc19-5b9e-4166-a898-99674fdf48aa","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"0-0"},{"bbox":[264,191,321,207],"type":"title","angle":0,"index":1,"text":"# 黄昭毅","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"level":1,"page_idx":0,"id":"9c17ecb1-d9f0-4c7f-82f1-125a3bb4bf01","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"0-1"},{"bbox":[128,229,456,239],"index":2,"angle":0,"type":"image","img_path":"/6dfbd8e0c314b83c59abc8da9987f3c5e1a2eb9495d05d8abc2aae5b80f3976c.jpg","color":{"line":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)","fill":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)"},"img_ratio":0.5512605042016807,"page_idx":0,"id":"24068c9e-7cef-4ea9-9730-49b25d85b617","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"0-2"},{"bbox":[58,250,285,309],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":3,"text":"振动的测量和分析，首先要求用振动传感器把机械的振动信号转换为电信号，然后通过放大，进行记录和显示。振动传感器有以下几项基本要求：","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":0,"id":"f1c00916-c9ef-4017-a625-8cec711327d5","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"0-3"},{"bbox":[58,314,283,341],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":4,"text":"1）具有较宽的动态范围，即对非常微弱和非常剧烈的振动都能精确地响应。","id":"c2b67cf7-1b9e-4196-89d6-d292a10d9af9","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":0,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"0-4"},{"bbox":[80,345,217,357],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":5,"text":"2）具有较宽的频率响应范围。","id":"e9c00f31-70f1-4a7c-9cd2-c65bd77cf583","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":0,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"0-5"},{"bbox":[80,361,276,373],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":6,"text":"3）在其频率响应范围内具有良好的线性度。","id":"15b4efcf-297b-4d4f-bb4b-4386bd0b6e39","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":0,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"0-6"},{"bbox":[80,377,277,389],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":7,"text":"4）抗干扰强，对环境变化有较低的灵敏度。","id":"f0aa5d01-e2dc-4091-b599-53dc1b457445","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":0,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"0-7"},{"bbox":[57,393,283,420],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":8,"text":"5）结构坚固，工作可靠，能够长时间保持稳定的性能。","id":"f0de1d30-ad03-4ec0-92a6-132c901d35b6","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":0,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"0-8"},{"bbox":[97,441,240,476],"type":"title","angle":0,"index":10,"text":"# 第1节 传感器的种类、原理和性能","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"level":1,"page_idx":0,"id":"717b3e88-4ff6-4ba4-82aa-e839acf81c6b","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"0-9"},{"bbox":[86,496,221,509],"type":"title","angle":0,"index":11,"text":"# （一）传感器的种类和原理","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"level":1,"page_idx":0,"id":"bf1c9a1c-cf1c-4b43-b823-6232d55443e2","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"0-10"},{"bbox":[56,518,282,563],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":12,"text":"振动传感器的种类很多，常用的有3种：即感受振动位移的位移传感器，感受振动速度的速度传感器，以及感受加速度的加速度传感器。","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":0,"id":"8d0d0fcd-0f5d-4378-a8c3-68daf658d7e1","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"0-11"},{"bbox":[55,565,280,656],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":13,"text":"振动位移、速度和加速度三者之间有着微分、积分关系。只要获得其中之一，便可换算求得另外两个参数。在选择测量参数时，通常应选择能得到最平坦的频率的参数，这样可以使测量仪器的可用动态范围最宽。图12-1-1为振动位移、速度和加速度频谱比较。","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":0,"id":"7a823fbc-223c-4da7-88a0-b8a1c529d2ee","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"0-12"},{"bbox":[77,660,154,671],"type":"title","angle":0,"index":14,"text":"# 1. 加速度传感器","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"level":1,"page_idx":0,"id":"0b2d8abc-c00b-4437-b659-e4392e05f9ff","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"0-13"},{"bbox":[55,676,280,767],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":15,"text":"目前应用最广的是压电式加速度计，由于它的频率范围与动态范围都比速度和位移传感器宽得多，因此在一般设备监测中总是优先选用。而且它体积小、重量轻、稳定性高；可以安装在任何方位，无需电源供电，自身产生信号；无移动元件，不易造成磨损，而且输出信号通过积分电路能容易","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":0,"id":"1b7e145e-a036-4b4f-a6b5-29ffbace6ae3","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"0-14"},{"bbox":[298,250,524,294],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":16,"text":"地转换成速度或位移信号。其不足之处是只有高阻输出。图12-1-2示出三种传感器频响和动态范围的比较。","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":0,"id":"ce932f8f-243f-4431-8a75-6827fbe753c8","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"0-15"},{"bbox":[315,309,511,490],"index":17,"angle":0,"type":"image","img_path":"/39918ad7dbd8e470061194b709eaaa761636be1e9176024aa13f093a22fa9129.jpg","color":{"line":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)","fill":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)"},"img_ratio":0.32941176470588235,"page_idx":0,"id":"879a3ea1-bc32-448c-9a27-3220fdbb3d66","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"0-16"},{"bbox":[320,500,496,511],"index":18,"angle":0,"type":"image_caption","text":"图12-1-1 振动位移、速度和加速度频谱比较","id":"8c377d3c-5bb4-41ea-b064-a03a49469495","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":0,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"0-17"},{"bbox":[310,528,498,747],"index":19,"angle":0,"type":"image","img_path":"/c7b77c47f4a5c7a5d18b18e09cd70b30608b7a50981567c68aa40f9bc8bd653c.jpg","color":{"line":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)","fill":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)"},"img_ratio":0.31596638655462184,"page_idx":0,"id":"36a88bd8-b594-403b-8141-78863229a790","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"0-18"},{"bbox":[323,756,490,768],"index":20,"angle":0,"type":"image_caption","text":"图12-1-2 不同传感器频响和动态范围比较","id":"a59137ec-43c3-4f01-a867-38cfca1bc35d","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":0,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"0-19"}],[{"bbox":[58,88,285,180],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":1,"text":"压电式加速度计的核心是压电晶体材料，通常是人工极化的铁电陶瓷。当受到机械应力时，不论是拉伸、压缩或剪切，在它的两个极板上会出现与所加应力成正比的电荷。当一个加速度计受到振动时，其内部质量块的惯性力就作用在压电晶体上，输出的电荷量与振动加速度成正比。","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":1,"id":"61995db4-4ee6-4934-a3a8-199eec56c08e","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"1-0"},{"bbox":[57,183,285,228],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":2,"text":"压电加速度计的结构（图12-1-3）主要有正置压缩式、倒置压缩式、环形剪切式和三角剪切式几种。","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":1,"id":"b5c29a4d-024c-46cd-9bdc-b4a37c986cfe","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"1-1"},{"bbox":[56,250,111,314],"index":3,"angle":0,"type":"image","img_path":"/4cf742ec0105f07251d60c135cf9016b159339fe265dc76a7185e07dd88dc2ce.jpg","color":{"line":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)","fill":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)"},"img_ratio":0.2,"page_idx":1,"id":"72c41adb-f42e-4738-a948-46cc12126d0d","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"1-2"},{"bbox":[63,320,86,331],"index":4,"angle":0,"type":"image_caption","text":"a）","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":1,"id":"e5f9cfab-e356-4994-92ae-11c0426726ab","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"1-3"},{"bbox":[117,255,168,314],"index":5,"angle":0,"type":"image","img_path":"/e1c5195db693f82f104eb0a3b3682786ba84a7591b95726c55e62fb35befc8f8.jpg","color":{"line":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)","fill":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)"},"img_ratio":0.2,"page_idx":1,"id":"ff3019fa-8fba-491f-ad61-d6f4972936d1","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"1-4"},{"bbox":[132,321,145,331],"index":6,"angle":0,"type":"image_caption","text":"b>","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":1,"id":"285661c2-e11f-4972-99bf-3dd021cd917f","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"1-5"},{"bbox":[173,255,230,315],"index":7,"angle":0,"type":"image","img_path":"/0cb30c002140c4c24ad02b56680c23f24d48bd1769a47f6a08f95da1a248e1bf.jpg","color":{"line":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)","fill":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)"},"img_ratio":0.2,"page_idx":1,"id":"4d99491c-4ec4-407e-87da-d4c637ad9616","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"1-6"},{"bbox":[190,323,202,332],"index":8,"angle":0,"type":"image_caption","text":"C）","id":"ce65dc59-01ac-4712-af61-2d80c22f4f4f","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":1,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"1-7"},{"bbox":[237,252,284,319],"index":9,"angle":0,"type":"image","img_path":"/8780fa5d22ce7644f1edff2527b84e8d38f354ab542259abb507e248c008c426.jpg","color":{"line":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)","fill":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)"},"img_ratio":0.2,"page_idx":1,"id":"f994e3ed-b454-4a05-b5d4-ac862503f181","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"1-8"},{"bbox":[251,324,264,333],"index":10,"angle":0,"type":"image_caption","text":"（）","id":"2cb699fb-c983-4129-9934-e441ca066c24","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":1,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"1-9"},{"bbox":[85,346,254,357],"index":11,"angle":0,"type":"image_caption","text":"图12-1-3 不同乐电加速度计的结构示意图","id":"641e87ae-9373-4c48-a462-942594df4cf9","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":1,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"1-10"},{"bbox":[82,359,255,368],"index":12,"angle":0,"type":"image_footnote","text":"a）正置压缩 b）倒置压缩 c）环形剪切","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"id":"a8388eca-4fca-4774-a407-e6a8ac076893","page_idx":1,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"1-11"},{"bbox":[143,372,194,381],"index":13,"angle":0,"type":"image_footnote","text":"6）△形剪切","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"id":"ff13ed6a-f1ea-4735-a6fa-d7a62bef0501","page_idx":1,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"1-12"},{"bbox":[76,397,145,409],"type":"title","angle":0,"index":15,"text":"# 2. 速度传感器","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"level":1,"page_idx":1,"id":"af2f2980-3301-45e5-87dc-218aaf448343","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"1-13"},{"bbox":[55,413,280,488],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":16,"text":"目前比较普遍的是磁电式速度传感器，其工作原理是电磁感应。当传感器承受振动时，它的线圈在磁场中运动而切割磁力线，产生感应电动势，形成电压输出，而该输出的电压正比于被测物体的速度，因此称为磁电式速度传感器。","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":1,"id":"f3a22424-7786-4e6a-b471-62bb274fb2e5","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"1-14"},{"bbox":[54,491,280,598],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":17,"text":"磁电式传感器灵敏度高，最适合用于测量振动量微小的高精度机械。它也可用作对相位误差要求较高的动平衡机或现场动平衡仪的讯号传感器。它的输出阻抗低，无需转换就可直接连接电压表及二次仪表。其缺点是体积较大，不适宜测量小的设备；频率范围窄，测量范围小；而且结构较复杂，在撞击下易损坏。","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":1,"id":"edf5b6df-eb3c-449c-8e17-49c9e7c19d17","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"1-15"},{"bbox":[74,602,252,615],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":18,"text":"磁电式速度传感器的结构示于图12-1-4。","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":1,"id":"67b84cef-5d8d-4956-b708-68aa411b8c50","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"1-16"},{"bbox":[99,640,233,712],"index":19,"angle":0,"type":"image","img_path":"/9ccbd34e0a749e0047f266e94abcd2107e2df551f84e8f1c51868375625b896a.jpg","color":{"line":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)","fill":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)"},"img_ratio":0.22521008403361345,"page_idx":1,"id":"4d17eceb-678b-483f-b94c-1c25135ec3a7","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"1-17"},{"bbox":[83,726,244,737],"index":20,"angle":0,"type":"image_caption","text":"图12-1-4磁电式速度传感器结构示意图","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":1,"id":"3ba21192-ab3f-4004-9319-5cea7e247cda","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"1-18"},{"bbox":[82,739,248,750],"index":21,"angle":0,"type":"image_footnote","text":"1—磁钢 2—线圈 3—阻尼环 4—弹簧片","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"id":"22b823ba-d401-4ad2-894f-be56746afcde","page_idx":1,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"1-19"},{"bbox":[105,752,224,763],"index":22,"angle":0,"type":"image_footnote","text":"5—芯轴 6—壳体 7—输出线","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"id":"066fe3af-130d-4d61-998e-5260da1cce28","page_idx":1,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"1-20"},{"bbox":[321,88,389,101],"type":"title","angle":0,"index":24,"text":"# 3. 位移传感器","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"level":1,"page_idx":1,"id":"f39135f9-59cc-40fd-9318-fb59ce693d38","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"1-21"},{"bbox":[298,103,525,197],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":25,"text":"目前应用最广的是电涡流位移传感器（图12-1-5），这是一种非接触式距离测量系统。它不断地测量传感器顶端与被测对象表面之间距离的变化，并使之转换成一个与之成正比的负直流电压。它既可单独测量静态位置或动态位移的变化，也可以同时测量静态位置和动态位移的变化。","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":1,"id":"d8b8cedd-eadf-4a66-b538-f70b6f80451b","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"1-22"},{"bbox":[295,213,524,416],"index":26,"angle":0,"type":"image","img_path":"/2fd00f345afc30b3d5186983c9970ea3192efa10149a580f0e08d2e8264740d8.jpg","color":{"line":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)","fill":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)"},"img_ratio":0.38487394957983195,"page_idx":1,"id":"269e0013-2423-45c7-a3ae-9921e12c6311","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"1-23"},{"bbox":[342,425,476,436],"index":27,"angle":0,"type":"image_caption","text":"图12-1-5 洞流传感器系统结构图","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":1,"id":"18e9193d-a4db-40c7-9a57-8b2ba95e4bef","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"1-24"},{"bbox":[307,437,509,475],"index":28,"angle":0,"type":"image_footnote","text":"1—传感器头部 2—传感器体 3—固定电缆 4—接插头 5—延长电缆 6—前置器 7—信号输出 8—电源电压 9—公共端","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"id":"5fb0e671-7f7b-416c-9a43-fe92ff553296","page_idx":1,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"1-25"},{"bbox":[293,484,520,575],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":29,"text":"电涡流传感器是根据涡电流原理工作的。传感器的顶部有一个小线圈，高频载频信号从此线圈产生一个磁场，该磁场感应的涡电流对磁场有相反的影响，并产生与间隙距离成正比的载频幅值，而解调器可把载频幅值的变化转换成低阻抗经校准的电压输出。","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":1,"id":"600d5547-7d63-4f40-b6a7-68b1e932b701","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"1-26"},{"bbox":[292,579,520,671],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":30,"text":"电涡流传感器在设备诊断中的作用主要是和前置器及有关电缆组成相位标记传感器系统。而相位标记所产生的信息可供测量转轴的转速、相位角、振动频率以及转轴的运动方向等，它能有助于鉴别不同的机械故障和对故障分类，再有就是在旋转机械的动平衡上起着重要的作用。","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":1,"id":"ce8306aa-1fa9-470b-87de-1aced80b5495","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"1-27"},{"bbox":[321,682,446,696],"type":"title","angle":0,"index":31,"text":"# （二）传感器的性能指标","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"level":1,"page_idx":1,"id":"22ce4c56-0050-4303-a399-119b58232f67","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"1-28"},{"bbox":[312,705,511,719],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":32,"text":"衡量传感器性能的主要技术指标有以下几个：","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":1,"id":"8c7115a3-b77b-4bff-8a01-ee8ffd089350","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"1-29"},{"bbox":[291,721,518,767],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":33,"text":"（1）灵敏度 传感器的灵敏度是它的输出电信号（电压、电荷等）同输入振动信号（加速度、速度、位移）的比值。例如，某只传感器灵敏度为","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":1,"id":"eadb53b0-28a8-465e-a270-826bfee45030","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"1-30"},{"bbox":[73,67,99,78],"type":"page_number","angle":0,"index":999999,"text":"12-2","color":{"line":"rgba(164, 164, 164, 1)","fill":"rgba(164, 164, 164, 1)"},"page_idx":1,"is_discarded":true,"id":"a1c5f81e-09a7-4774-b953-bed6ece26e17","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"1-31"}],[{"bbox":[60,92,285,121],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":1,"text":"$100\\mathrm{mV / cm / s}$  （峰），表示当振动速度峰值为  $1\\mathrm{cm}/$  s时，传感器输出  $100\\mathrm{mV}$  电压信号。","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":2,"id":"88fc1f30-42d9-455f-af8c-eea393e4412e","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"2-0"},{"bbox":[59,123,284,152],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":2,"text":"测量弱振动时，传感器的灵敏度应高一些。因为灵敏度越高，可以测量的下限值越低。","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":2,"id":"cb28e713-3b29-4ed1-9c0a-c4d9b0d6347c","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"2-1"},{"bbox":[58,154,284,183],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":3,"text":"（2）横向灵敏度 横向灵敏度是指传感器对横向振动与轴向振动的响应之比值","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":2,"id":"e254fb7a-cc96-4aed-8305-ad9d3016b58e","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"2-2"},{"bbox":[86,186,238,210],"type":"interline_equation","angle":0,"index":4,"text":"$$\nS_{\\text{横}} = \\frac{\\text{输出} / \\text{单位横向振动}}{\\text{输出} / \\text{单位轴向振动}}\\times 100\\%\n$$","color":{"line":"rgba(230, 122, 171, 1)","fill":"rgba(230, 122, 171, 1)"},"page_idx":2,"id":"868adb98-0b2d-451a-bf29-f9e677f56d05","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"2-3"},{"bbox":[57,213,283,241],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":5,"text":"在振动测量中，传感器的横向灵敏度越小越好。","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":2,"id":"c8ca0d1f-5d1b-4f47-8218-0414f1d3c19f","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"2-4"},{"bbox":[57,245,283,288],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":6,"text":"（3）测量范围 它表示输出信号与输入信号保持线性关系的输入信号幅度变化范围，即传感器可测量的最小振动与最大振动之间的范围。","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":2,"id":"4e388b5e-5c41-4857-9ee7-e466b3576d0d","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"2-5"},{"bbox":[57,292,283,351],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":7,"text":"传感器信号不应超过其测量范围，否则要造成损坏或较大误差。测量微振时，要考虑传感器和二次仪表所组成的系统能分辨的最小输入信号值，使信号和噪声之比大于10。","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":2,"id":"0a44b46f-744c-44ba-b6df-7e15160a633c","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"2-6"},{"bbox":[54,355,282,505],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":8,"text":"（4）频率特性（频率响应）范围 它是一个很重要的技术指标，当被测信号频率超过传感器（或系统）的使用频率范围时，会产生很大的测量误差。例如，某只传感器的灵敏度指标为  $100\\mathrm{Pe} / \\mathrm{g}$  规定误差为  $\\pm 5\\%$  ，那末，如图12-1-6所示，在  $f_{1}$  和  $f_{2}$  之间的任意频率点上，其灵敏度  $S$  在  $95\\mathrm{Pe} / \\mathrm{g}$  至 $105\\mathrm{Pe} / \\mathrm{g}$  的范围内。而在  $f_{1}$  和  $f_{2}$  之外的频率点上，灵敏度的误差将超过  $5\\%$  。  $f_{0}$  是传感器的共振频率，一般选取  $f_{2} = \\left(\\frac{1}{3}\\sim \\frac{1}{5}\\right)f_{0}$","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":2,"id":"b6ffe824-538d-46b4-ba84-ab5e9b4b932d","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"2-7"},{"bbox":[66,527,263,628],"index":9,"angle":0,"type":"image","img_path":"/6339a336ba6f6986a2418799b5c798db175faf229ced2725b9602d3b1cbf3eed.jpg","color":{"line":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)","fill":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)"},"img_ratio":0.3310924369747899,"page_idx":2,"id":"dc0d6bd3-6e62-4f90-a4a7-de3529b6e9c8","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"2-8"},{"bbox":[105,637,221,650],"index":10,"angle":0,"type":"image_caption","text":"图12-1-6 加速度频率响应图","id":"3ddd4dcc-783d-4b20-ab8b-b7ef8e034afb","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":2,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"2-9"},{"bbox":[48,657,276,717],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":11,"text":"（5）温度范围 传感器一般是工作在常温条件下，即  $0^{\\circ} \\mathrm{C} \\sim 40^{\\circ} \\mathrm{C}$  左右。环境温度超过给定的温度范围就会引起传感器的损坏或造成较大的测量误差。","id":"db16c6d4-b74d-4fa7-b0c1-d9ec0f013e5b","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":2,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"2-10"},{"bbox":[48,721,276,766],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":12,"text":"（6）重量一般要求被测物体的重量要大于传感器重量的10倍，否则会由于附加了传感器的重量，使被测物体的振动状态将发生变化。","id":"793f5176-1c04-4f9e-9d49-a236213379ab","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":2,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"2-11"},{"bbox":[339,107,477,123],"type":"title","angle":0,"index":14,"text":"# 第2节 传感器的选择","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"level":1,"page_idx":2,"id":"eb5d9de5-3fe3-4abc-9a3d-67b19fb3d385","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"2-12"},{"bbox":[298,138,523,182],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":15,"text":"传感器的选择除应以其性能的主要技术指标为依据，还需考虑与前置放大器及电缆系统的匹配关系。","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":2,"id":"7f827dc2-9554-4f5b-9b7f-9e211a2083dd","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"2-13"},{"bbox":[297,186,523,261],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":16,"text":"由于加速度计的信号功率非常小，容易迅速耗散，而且它的输出阻抗很高，电流和电压基本上是反相位。为调整这种状态，就需要配上前置放大器。它还可以通过把信号“调节”到基准灵敏度的方法，用以补偿非标准的传感器灵敏度。","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":2,"id":"e67ba703-0848-4748-bc06-292aa0e3ce5a","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"2-14"},{"bbox":[295,265,522,357],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":17,"text":"前置放大器有电压放大器和电荷放大器两种，应用最广的是电荷放大器。它可以固定于任何位置，把加速度计输出的高阻抗的电荷量变换成低阻抗的电压量，并加以放大。由于传感器的低频范围受到电荷放大器频率下限的限制，所以在选用电荷放大器时需考虑性能指标的匹配。","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":2,"id":"1f9f9a86-6cef-4561-a96e-67c0b1edc3e5","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"2-15"},{"bbox":[294,359,520,451],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":18,"text":"电缆连接系统也是同样影响传感器最佳性能的重要因素，由于电缆的布线电容与灵敏度和低频特性无关，一般传感器和电荷放大器之间的实用电缆长度以  $100\\sim 200\\mathrm{m}$  为限，而在电荷放大器后面的电缆长度则不受限制。这都是由于电荷放大器具有以下一些优点：","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":2,"id":"16dc08f4-fbfd-4f50-8cd3-7da8076534f5","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"2-16"},{"bbox":[293,454,519,480],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":19,"text":"1）当所用的电缆长度有变化时，可不必重新校正。","id":"bad5e312-1dc1-4e15-a3cf-e4d34ec8894e","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":2,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"2-17"},{"bbox":[293,485,518,512],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":20,"text":"2）在一定的限度内，可以使用不降低灵敏度的长电缆。","id":"24d174da-7ea8-4917-b444-577c1c39f478","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":2,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"2-18"},{"bbox":[293,517,518,544],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":21,"text":"3）传感器和电缆的绝缘电阻不必像电压放大器那样高。","id":"fa5f9d2f-db26-4a24-a647-a7945c4bb2ff","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":2,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"2-19"},{"bbox":[291,548,518,591],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":22,"text":"4）灵敏度的温度特性只影响传感器的电荷灵敏度的温度特性，而与电缆电容的温度特性无关。","id":"fb4c22f9-ef5b-463a-a923-aff885b5437c","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":2,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"2-20"},{"bbox":[291,596,518,625],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":24,"text":"在选择和应用传感器时，还可以从以下3种传感器的优缺点对比中，取得最佳选择。","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":2,"id":"4cfe30dd-b4e8-4391-848d-975041b14060","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"2-21"},{"bbox":[320,637,445,651],"type":"title","angle":0,"index":25,"text":"# （一）电涡流位移传感器","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"level":1,"page_idx":2,"id":"dbaca5f5-f4a9-4089-b1c2-b6dc9ba5e027","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"2-22"},{"bbox":[315,660,365,671],"type":"title","angle":0,"index":26,"text":"# （1）优点","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"level":1,"page_idx":2,"id":"6ea3bb0c-98ba-4c5e-afe6-6a2faab8d68e","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"2-23"},{"bbox":[289,676,516,719],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":27,"text":"1）直接测量转轴的振动运动。这是回转机械最常见的故障源，如不平衡、不对中、磨损、轴承不稳定等。","id":"e8e293a5-3ae6-4ddb-bc1f-7ffd1be13d46","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":2,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"2-24"},{"bbox":[289,724,515,768],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":28,"text":"2）测量转轴在轴承间隙内相对于轴承或轴承座的平均位置。这是对转子稳态单向预载的重要指示，如不对中、流体力或气动力的影响等。","id":"3ff290e6-7942-47d0-9e93-7db40eba5218","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":2,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"2-25"},{"bbox":[489,69,512,79],"type":"page_number","angle":0,"index":999999,"text":"72-3","color":{"line":"rgba(164, 164, 164, 1)","fill":"rgba(164, 164, 164, 1)"},"page_idx":2,"is_discarded":true,"id":"f525770a-c306-4cd4-a2a7-6b6750886650","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"2-26"}],[{"bbox":[78,63,104,74],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":0,"text":"12-4","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":3,"id":"a9c65bed-c732-46d9-9322-273cc0e75536","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"3-0"},{"bbox":[64,85,289,112],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":1,"text":"3）容易校准。只需用螺旋千分表和数字电压表进行静态校准。","id":"995bab7e-e15f-450f-8637-80dc15394750","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":3,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"3-1"},{"bbox":[64,117,289,144],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":2,"text":"4）直接用工程单位测量位移，这是评定机器响应和振动烈度最有用的单位。","id":"6e36c478-5ee3-46ca-ad6f-cb9b3f2dd6cd","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":3,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"3-2"},{"bbox":[63,149,288,175],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":3,"text":"5）信噪比高，可在  $300\\mathrm{m}$  外分离出高电压低阻抗的输出。","id":"9766cce8-fa8d-4241-857c-efdc7dc35517","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":3,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"3-3"},{"bbox":[86,180,236,191],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":4,"text":"6）频响范围宽广，从  $0\\sim 10\\mathrm{kHz}$","id":"46d88d9b-dfef-4321-948b-6a12b1ebe1a1","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":3,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"3-4"},{"bbox":[85,196,201,207],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":5,"text":"7）固态结构，可靠性好。","id":"ede167a8-8c70-4095-96dd-6984ed48368b","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":3,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"3-5"},{"bbox":[85,211,271,223],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":6,"text":"8）采用模块系统设计，更换零组件方便。","id":"fee610db-ffd5-4585-aa1e-78455307cf8c","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":3,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"3-6"},{"bbox":[88,227,136,239],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":8,"text":"（2）缺点","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":3,"id":"5b0459b0-86e2-49b9-a5f7-316416176b22","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"3-7"},{"bbox":[63,243,287,271],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":9,"text":"1）转轴材质不均、表面粗糙度、划痕、锈斑以及局部磁场都会引起机械和电气的跳动。","id":"1ab987dd-0b00-44bb-88c4-e11dc918b4ee","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":3,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"3-8"},{"bbox":[84,274,260,286],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":10,"text":"2）对某些轴材料的金相成分表现敏感。","id":"b4bc58d3-76bd-46c9-bba2-623d36676502","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":3,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"3-9"},{"bbox":[84,289,189,301],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":11,"text":"3）需要外部直流电源。","id":"a241b39d-d26c-4517-8255-f86bd7b785d5","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":3,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"3-10"},{"bbox":[84,305,270,317],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":12,"text":"4）在某些机器结构中，可能不便于安装。","id":"9e152770-08e6-4b42-9d43-09e50b21b93f","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":3,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"3-11"},{"bbox":[61,321,286,348],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":13,"text":"5）临时要求固定电涡流传感器比较困难，因此最好是永久性安装。","id":"92dfa161-8b58-44f7-abea-79f74ec5cf9d","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":3,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"3-12"},{"bbox":[60,352,286,380],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":14,"text":"6）用于机械阻抗小的机器，必须在同一位置处与地震式传感器联合使用。","id":"f134cfd6-cbbc-498f-9377-926ba77bde20","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":3,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"3-13"},{"bbox":[89,392,179,405],"type":"title","angle":0,"index":16,"text":"# （二）速度传感器","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"level":1,"page_idx":3,"id":"d143211b-8a10-4f0b-96f1-891a67a9f988","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"3-14"},{"bbox":[85,415,133,426],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":17,"text":"（1）优点","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":3,"id":"3541cacf-bf53-4d06-8683-2a789147d495","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"3-15"},{"bbox":[83,431,227,442],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":18,"text":"1）容易固定安装在机器的外部。","id":"22441078-0ce4-4d24-b7e3-871932abf3be","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":3,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"3-16"},{"bbox":[82,447,242,458],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":19,"text":"2）在  $15\\sim 1\\mathrm{kHz}$  中频范围信号较强。","id":"9688e91c-8213-4cd5-af23-e85f1110ddaf","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":3,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"3-17"},{"bbox":[82,462,238,474],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":20,"text":"3）自身产生信号，无需外部电源。","id":"58b874a9-fa76-4323-a371-7113369a866e","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":3,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"3-18"},{"bbox":[59,479,283,505],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":21,"text":"4）与电涡流传感器组合使用，可以测量轴的绝对运动。","id":"f2d97f55-d287-4a6f-a01c-2377dcd00d41","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":3,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"3-19"},{"bbox":[81,510,196,522],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":22,"text":"5）可以用磁铁临时固定。","id":"5b5e5ad6-2aca-4c1c-8a75-7b43e7b8a161","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":3,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"3-20"},{"bbox":[81,525,277,538],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":23,"text":"6）频响适于中等转速回转机械的整体评价。","id":"34b3f256-f45c-484f-a394-c82a31212527","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":3,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"3-21"},{"bbox":[81,541,236,554],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":24,"text":"7）传感器适合在中等温度下使用。","id":"cbbb9fa0-52e1-449c-bffc-f119404c4e5d","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":3,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"3-22"},{"bbox":[81,557,195,569],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":25,"text":"8）速度容易积分成位移。","id":"880c73be-5a9e-4a5d-b784-418bf768b26f","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":3,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"3-23"},{"bbox":[83,573,131,584],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":27,"text":"（2）缺点","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":3,"id":"4952bd8b-93cb-428c-b59d-bc4413bbb668","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"3-24"},{"bbox":[57,589,282,616],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":28,"text":"1）提供动态运动信息有限，要求机械阻抗较小。","id":"7f323b9c-7c27-4080-9e26-e513e3624a0c","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":3,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"3-25"},{"bbox":[57,620,282,647],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":29,"text":"2）固定在机器外部，易受管路、基础及邻近机器振动的影响。","id":"f749a89d-1b60-4e2f-b281-a8efff40d74e","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":3,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"3-26"},{"bbox":[56,652,281,679],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":30,"text":"3）在使用一段时间后，其机械结构和性能将降级。","id":"4d9608c1-e088-417c-aeaa-01b2c37bb15d","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":3,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"3-27"},{"bbox":[56,684,281,710],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":31,"text":"4）当传感器结构出现故障，则要求更换整个组件。","id":"ced2dc19-c3e2-4210-aa58-5bf21c4fd3fb","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":3,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"3-28"},{"bbox":[78,715,224,728],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":33,"text":"5）校准较困难，需从机上拆下。","id":"95baf646-20af-4cc7-95c3-09c4a0b3e1a2","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":3,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"3-29"},{"bbox":[78,731,224,743],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":34,"text":"6）低频时会引入幅值和相位差。","id":"708dad42-699d-433c-bf70-e5fc87242121","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":3,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"3-30"},{"bbox":[78,747,233,759],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":35,"text":"7）在大幅值时，横向灵敏度不好。","id":"a8df14cb-2c3a-4e6a-bc85-4ac3b203d004","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":3,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"3-31"},{"bbox":[327,85,441,97],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":37,"text":"8）体积较大，比较笨重。","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":3,"id":"4c1903a5-1004-46ec-b709-f14d3cd6744f","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"3-32"},{"bbox":[333,110,411,123],"type":"title","angle":0,"index":38,"text":"# （三）加速度计","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"level":1,"page_idx":3,"id":"d115b05c-71e2-4c46-ac93-3b752fd96eef","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"3-33"},{"bbox":[329,133,377,144],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":39,"text":"（1）优点","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":3,"id":"3fab6b4b-1b2b-4616-837e-c462b6c2310b","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"3-34"},{"bbox":[326,149,511,160],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":40,"text":"1）当固定于机器外部时，比较容易安装。","id":"ecc89f33-5512-4541-8ad5-78001d597e3d","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":3,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"3-35"},{"bbox":[326,165,515,176],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":41,"text":"2）特别适合于  $2\\mathrm{kHz}$  以上高频振动的测量。","id":"5fc26303-9956-4f87-b02f-3339672b222c","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":3,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"3-36"},{"bbox":[326,181,440,192],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":42,"text":"3）无活动件，可靠性好。","id":"9cf92813-2e22-46d9-893e-81f7b5f149c4","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":3,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"3-37"},{"bbox":[325,197,490,208],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":43,"text":"4）能适用于高温及放射性辐照场所。","id":"2ced1374-5137-4be2-bfdc-17647849aafc","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":3,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"3-38"},{"bbox":[325,213,500,224],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":44,"text":"5）可超过某一最高频率和温度的限制。","id":"0f456f3f-ca9a-433b-9321-71975f1d9dd5","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":3,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"3-39"},{"bbox":[325,228,399,239],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":45,"text":"6）重量相当轻。","id":"6420ac3f-d56d-4fdc-8370-8c97732169fa","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":3,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"3-40"},{"bbox":[327,245,376,255],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":47,"text":"（2）缺点","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":3,"id":"aeebefc8-4b9d-45f7-81ea-17d6b030e6ab","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"3-41"},{"bbox":[301,260,526,287],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":48,"text":"1）提供动态运动信息有限，要求机械阻抗较小。","id":"e85fdb4e-b1c8-4eaa-869e-c911c280ed6c","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":3,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"3-42"},{"bbox":[301,292,525,319],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":49,"text":"2）固定在机器外部，易受管路、基础及邻近机器振动的影响。","id":"0479c79a-aaba-460a-8002-f24758c76fbb","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":3,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"3-43"},{"bbox":[300,323,525,350],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":50,"text":"3）容易因与机器的接触或固定不良而产生噪声影响。","id":"2e8d6efc-c701-45c4-b431-47e31943406f","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":3,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"3-44"},{"bbox":[300,355,525,382],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":51,"text":"4）当传感器结构出现故障，需要更换整个组件。","id":"032e52eb-0515-4749-bd77-9f1f946e8c19","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":3,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"3-45"},{"bbox":[323,387,468,399],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":52,"text":"5）校准较困难，需从机上拆下。","id":"4007ba34-e6b4-42f6-af93-8c070123b236","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":3,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"3-46"},{"bbox":[323,403,518,414],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":53,"text":"6）难以用于某些低速机器和低频振动测量。","id":"cbe9f749-df2d-42b5-a40e-3e0f09b920a3","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":3,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"3-47"},{"bbox":[299,418,523,445],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":54,"text":"7）需经两次积分才得位移，容易出现噪声问题。","id":"e2770c40-da09-40e9-a3e5-ccaeadff347d","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":3,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"3-48"},{"bbox":[322,450,417,462],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":55,"text":"8）要求有外部电源，","id":"7b847a65-ceab-49b1-8798-de68ede8925d","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":3,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"3-49"},{"bbox":[325,484,490,499],"type":"title","angle":0,"index":57,"text":"# 第3节 传感器的安装要点","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"level":1,"page_idx":3,"id":"f746b10e-7843-4e85-b342-b40f2874538f","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"3-50"},{"bbox":[327,520,486,533],"type":"title","angle":0,"index":58,"text":"# （一）加速度计安装位置的选择","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"level":1,"page_idx":3,"id":"d2e34db7-86c8-4bd0-979d-ee6b200c9505","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"3-51"},{"bbox":[297,543,523,602],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":59,"text":"由于加速度计的主要灵敏度是在轴向，其横向灵敏度较小，仅为轴向的  $1\\% \\sim 3\\%$  ，因此在安装加速度计时需注意其轴向应与要测量的方向相一致。","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":3,"id":"b1a49eee-5aaa-4b2a-96fe-5bb95d31e8ce","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"3-52"},{"bbox":[296,607,522,666],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":60,"text":"测点的位置通常取决于振动测量的目的。例如，为了监测转轴及轴承的运转状况，可如图12-3-1所示，在轴承的外壳上安装加速度计，其安装原则是加速度计应安装在振动直接传达的通道上。","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":3,"id":"4f83f713-8557-400d-967d-9be20fc1aa0a","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"3-53"},{"bbox":[295,670,521,761],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":61,"text":"由图12-3-1可见，回转部件产生的振动是通过轴承传给轴承座。在  $A$  、  $C$  处测量比在  $B$  、  $D$  处测量，其传达通道要短，而且在  $B$  、  $D$  测量的信号还可能混杂着机器其它部位传来的讯号。就滚动轴承而言，一般测量一个轴向和一个径向振动，即可获得其运行状况的有用信息。","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":3,"id":"d93d77e8-cdb0-4cb8-b23a-111153e061ad","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"3-54"}],[{"bbox":[118,110,455,287],"index":1,"angle":0,"type":"image","img_path":"/34b5f2c28ed2012a70534171e481a581383b7f47071d36db6fae90f406ac3db4.jpg","color":{"line":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)","fill":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)"},"img_ratio":0.5663865546218487,"page_idx":4,"id":"f507e979-e4c5-4c57-a45c-d0758adcb2e9","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"4-0"},{"bbox":[207,295,367,307],"index":2,"angle":0,"type":"image_caption","text":"图12-3-1 加速度计灵敏度及安装位置图","id":"e5333b97-3b34-4ce5-964f-5a62e323a2bc","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":4,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"4-1"},{"bbox":[84,327,243,341],"type":"title","angle":0,"index":3,"text":"# （二）加速度计安装方法的选择","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"level":1,"page_idx":4,"id":"349e3a86-812b-4f1a-ab42-fdf354c94865","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"4-2"},{"bbox":[55,350,280,378],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":4,"text":"加速度计的安装与使用方式不同，其频率特性也不一样，不同的安装及特性列于表12-3-1。","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":4,"id":"87461814-5353-4ac9-bb13-527fe4a9dcfc","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"4-3"},{"bbox":[55,381,282,458],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":5,"text":"1）凡用于长期状态监测以及对故障信号需作频谱分析，且对高频信号有需要时，应尽量采用双头螺栓牢固地固定在监测点上。有些监测点也可以只有双头螺栓，而不安装传感器，以供巡回点检使用。","id":"471d6f3d-f383-4160-9bc8-7a6393d27315","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":4,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"4-4"},{"bbox":[55,460,281,505],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":6,"text":"2）磁吸座固定仅适用于低频，振动较大超过  $1\\mathrm{kHz}$  就难以吸牢。当测量微振低加速度，最多可使用到  $2\\mathrm{kHz}$  。","id":"a9d7c018-4d26-4278-8f39-af56326764f1","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":4,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"4-5"},{"bbox":[55,507,281,536],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":7,"text":"3）巡回点检用的便携式仪器，常在手持式探针中装有加速度传感器，使用中应注意：","id":"5034091f-0828-4b2f-aa22-3571a49a16f9","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":4,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"4-6"},{"bbox":[294,318,520,346],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":9,"text":"① 手持探针应垂直于测量点基线，如果倾斜就会造成较大的测量误差。","id":"2ff8cbb6-1325-4b7d-bc6b-d0ea236a6d2c","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":4,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"4-7"},{"bbox":[294,350,520,378],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":10,"text":"② 每次测量必须在同一位置同一方向，稍有移动也会造成很大的测量误差。","id":"d115def6-b4a0-4a18-9ff2-b590f0d3042f","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":4,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"4-8"},{"bbox":[294,381,520,426],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":11,"text":"③ 探针抵触测点要用力适中，不可过猛使基座应变造成输出增大，也不可太轻因虚接触引起冲击振动。","id":"b2a6f8c0-2068-4239-8dfe-ec92e5c6ffd9","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":4,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"4-9"},{"bbox":[294,429,520,473],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":12,"text":"④ 要防止发生接触共振现象，一般只适宜测量  $1\\mathrm{kHz}$  以下的振动，对高频振动信号则损耗较大。","id":"e05eeeba-8600-4e72-adae-bd01e5bfcc9d","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":4,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"4-10"},{"bbox":[294,477,520,536],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":13,"text":"4）有时由于加速度计及测量仪器各自接地，会产生接地回路电流，引起测量误差，可在传感器与安装表面之间加云母片或绝缘片，采用绝缘螺栓，以切断接地回路。","id":"b7a33ad8-7072-4197-8c22-e690945c48fe","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":4,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"4-11"},{"bbox":[199,548,374,561],"index":15,"angle":0,"type":"table_caption","text":"表12-3-1 加速度计的安装方法及特征","id":"bda6c514-e3a7-44d1-b94e-0cb64f9c007a","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":4,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"4-12"},{"bbox":[55,564,522,775],"index":16,"angle":0,"type":"table_body","img_path":"/","id":"308c45b2-14dc-4236-9664-3ce6b11f8309","color":{"line":"rgba(103, 194, 63, 1)","fill":"rgba(103, 194, 63, 1)"},"table_body":"<table><tr><td>安 装 方 法</td><td>特 征</td></tr><tr><td>钢制双头螺栓</td><td>这是最好的安装法,有即将传感器与被测体看成为整体</td></tr><tr><td>绝缘体绝缘螺栓</td><td>用绝缘螺栓固定,其特点与钢制双头螺栓相同。但用于需要电气绝缘时</td></tr><tr><td>刚性高的绝缘垫粘接剂(可用快速粘接剂)</td><td>用粘接剂固定,和绝缘法一样、频率特性良好,可达到10kHz水平</td></tr><tr><td>刚性高的蜡</td><td>用蜡固定,频率特性好,缺点是不耐温</td></tr><tr><td>绝缘磁铁</td><td>用磁铁固定,仅适用于1~2kHz的频率</td></tr><tr><td>探针</td><td>用手持探针,仅用于1000Hz以内的频率</td></tr></table>","page_idx":4,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"4-13"},{"bbox":[485,71,509,81],"type":"page_number","angle":0,"index":999999,"text":"12-5","color":{"line":"rgba(164, 164, 164, 1)","fill":"rgba(164, 164, 164, 1)"},"page_idx":4,"is_discarded":true,"id":"d1ebd468-d955-4eef-a3b2-b54a38a2495b","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"4-14"}],[{"bbox":[465,95,486,106],"index":1,"angle":0,"type":"table_caption","lines_deleted":true,"text":"","id":"bda6c514-e3a7-44d1-b94e-0cb64f9c007a","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":5,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"5-0"},{"bbox":[47,109,515,543],"index":2,"angle":0,"type":"table_body","lines_deleted":true,"text":"","id":"308c45b2-14dc-4236-9664-3ce6b11f8309","color":{"line":"rgba(103, 194, 63, 1)","fill":"rgba(103, 194, 63, 1)"},"table_body":"","page_idx":5,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"5-1"},{"bbox":[61,73,86,83],"type":"page_number","angle":0,"index":999999,"text":"12-6","color":{"line":"rgba(164, 164, 164, 1)","fill":"rgba(164, 164, 164, 1)"},"page_idx":5,"is_discarded":true,"id":"74628409-f20a-46fa-89a5-6a68dfa2b6c9","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"5-2"}]],"mergeConnections":[{"id":"bda6c514-e3a7-44d1-b94e-0cb64f9c007a","blocks":["4-12","5-0"],"type":"merge"},{"id":"308c45b2-14dc-4236-9664-3ce6b11f8309","blocks":["4-13","5-1"],"type":"merge"}]}